            <h3 class="h5">In-Office Team</h3>
          </div>

          <div class="text-box">

            <p>StaffViz optimizes productivity with comprehensive monitoring and management tools. Efficient task
              allocation, progress tracking, and analysis promote a culture of collaboration.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
